/.servo
# `.cargo/config.toml` is now local-dev-only (gitignored): serval needs no
# committed build settings (the inherited servo target linkers / RUSTC_BOOTSTRAP
# were verified unused), so the file holds only local path overrides, like
# `repos/mere/.cargo/config.toml`.
/.cargo/
# Don't commit Cargo.lock (any workspace, any depth). The owned forks
# (mark-ik/netrender, nova, boa) are `branch = ...` git deps; a committed lock
# would pin them to a dev-history commit that goes stale as we develop. Tracking
# their branch tips (and resolving crates.io deps to the latest matching release)
# is what keeps the dependency landscape current rather than expiring on a pin.
# Load-bearing upstreams we don't own (servo/stylo) stay rev-pinned in Cargo.toml.
Cargo.lock
# cargo-check / reftest log artifacts (root + per-crate, any depth): test
# outputs, reftest dumps, pass/fail lists. The committed cargo-check-env.ps1
# (mozjs build-env script) is the one thing kept.
**/.cargo-check-logs/**
!**/.cargo-check-logs/cargo-check-env.ps1
# WPT run logs (per-port, any depth): local test output, never committed.
**/.wpt-logs/
/.rustup
/.servobuild
/.wpt
/.vs
/android-toolchains
/target
# Generated wasm-bindgen browser worker artifacts. Source lives in
# components/serval-scripted-worker and support/build-scripted-workers.ps1.
/dist/scripted-workers/
# Sub-workspace build outputs. Each of these crates has its own
# [workspace], so the root `/target` (anchored) doesn't cover them.
# Explicit paths on purpose: a blanket `target/` would also ignore the
# tracked WPT test resource at
# tests/wpt/.../the-form-element/resources/target (a real test dir, not
# build output).
/components/script-engine-boa/target
/probes/*/target
/tests/wpt/reftests-report/report.html
/python/_virtualenv*
/python/_venv*
/python/tidy/servo_tidy.egg-info
/tests/wpt/sync
/tests/wpt/**/**/.cache/
/tests/dromaeo/dromaeo
*.pkl
*.pyc
*.swp
*.swo
*.csv
*.rej
*.orig
.coverage
.DS_Store
Servo.app
servo.pftrace
.config.mk.last
/glfw
webrender-captures/
/screenshots
/etc/notarization/

# Python setuptools
/servo.egg-info

# Allow CSV files to be used as resources in tests
!/tests/**/*.csv

